Thu Oct 19 16:24:31 CEST 2000 Paolo Molaro <lupus@debian.org>

	* Gtk::Widget::parent may return undef.
	* Gtk/Gtk.pm: allow -init in use Gtk -init;
	* Gtk/xs/GtkList.xs GtkTree.xs: applied patch from 
